      "answer": "You can find information about campus maps and staying safe on campus on the UTS website under the campus resources section. Campus maps help you find your way to buildings, transport, and amenities, and there is also information on how to stay safe on campus and what to do in an emergency [2]. Additionally, safety and security details, including emergency contacts and campus help points, are available to support your safety and wellbeing [1].",
