      "question": "Can I complete the Juris Doctor fully online at UTS?",
      "answer": "No, the Juris Doctor (JD) degree at UTS is NOT delivered fully online. While many subjects offer options for online study, some subjects do require on-campus attendance. The degree can be completed by day or evening, in part-time or full-time mode, with some subjects offered in weekend or intensive blocks [2].",
