      "answer": "If you are an international student, you should get in touch by completing the international student enquiry form. The information you provide in this form will be used to respond to your enquiry and may also be used to provide you with general information about the university. Please refer to the privacy policies for details. Fields marked with an asterisk (*) are required [1][2][3][4][5][6].",
