        "https://www.uts.edu.au/for-students/current-students/managing-your-course/current-students-information-business/study-and-assessment-resources/effective-time-management",
        "https://www.uts.edu.au/for-students/current-students/support/helps/self-help-resources/postgraduate-resources/how-write-research-proposal",
