      "answer": "If you have accepted your offer and enrolled in subjects, to defer your offer you need to submit an ASK UTS Online Enquiry. When you submit a request to defer your offer, you will be withdrawn from any enrolled subjects for the relevant session. You do not need to submit a course withdrawal request when deferring your offer [1][2][3].",
