      "question": "What should I include in the body of my assignment when I'm developing my argument?",
      "answer": "When developing your argument in the body of your assignment, you should include the following:\n\n- Each paragraph should focus on one stage or point of your argument, clearly articulated with a topic sentence that introduces the main idea of that paragraph.  \n- Follow the topic sentence with supplementary or supporting sentences that provide evidence, examples, and explanations to back up your point.  \n- Structure your argument logically so that each paragraph builds on the previous one, helping to clearly communicate your overall position.  \n- Make sure each stage of your argument is reflected in the structure of your paper, with one stage per paragraph [3], [5].",
