      "question": "What kinds of careers could I have with a science degree at UTS?",
      "answer": "With a science degree from UTS, you can pursue a wide range of careers in various fields. Science jobs can take you anywhere from laboratories to national parks, the ocean, or even outer space, offering limitless possibilities [1]. UTS is ranked among the top 5 universities in Australia and the world\u2019s top 100 for graduate employment outcomes, providing a strong foundation for a lifelong career in science [2]. The degree prepares you for professional roles involving lab work, scientific reporting, communication, and practical application of knowledge [4]. Additionally, UTS offers hands-on learning and work-integrated learning opportunities to prepare you for your future career [3].",
      "reference": "A science degree can lead to careers in diverse sectors, including business, government, health and education. The text also mentions roles linked to areas like cancer treatment, renewable energy, biostatistics, and crime scene investigation.",
