      "answer": "To request a student conduct report for LPAB admission, you need to send the following details to Law.PE@uts.edu.au: your Full Name, Date of Birth, and Student Number. You should only request the conduct report after your degree is completed and all results are finalised, as reports prepared beforehand will not meet LPAB requirements. Additionally, conduct reports are only valid for 6 months, so you should request it when you are preparing documentation for your application [1][4].",
