      "question": "How do I join Conversations@UTS, and what is it for?",
      "answer": "To join Conversations@UTS, you can simply turn up to a session that suits you\u2014no prior registration is needed. Check the session times on the HELPS web page or the timetable provided online to find a convenient time, either on campus or via Zoom [2][3].\n\nConversations@UTS is designed to help you practise your English conversation skills in a friendly and relaxed environment. It brings together international students and local volunteers for casual conversations to develop your confidence in social, university, and work settings [1][2][3][4][5].",
      "reference": "Just turn up to a session and check the HELPS web page for session times. Conversations@ UTS helps students practise English conversation skills, meet new people, and build confidence in casual conversations at university, socially, and at work.",
