      "answer": "The recommended way to collect your testamur if you\u2019re eligible to attend a graduation ceremony is to collect your printed graduation documents in person at your graduation ceremony. Proxy collection is also possible but requires an appointment at the UTS Student Centre. Alternatively, you can opt for a testamur mailout (domestically or internationally), though an administrative charge applies for postage [3].",
